Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">[colony/] Found Syndicate Colony</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="s62"><Data ss:Type="String">[colony/] Założono kolonię Syndykatu</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="s62"/><Cell ss:StyleID="s62"/><Cell ss:StyleID="s62"/><Cell ss:StyleID="s62"/></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0" ss:Height="60"><Cell ss:StyleID="s62"><Data ss:Type="String">FOUND_SYNDICATE_COLONY</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="s62"><Data ss:Type="String">DESCRIPTION</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">{XML_UNITPROPERTIES_STRATEGIC@FOUND_COLONY@SHARED_DESCRIPTION}</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="s62"><Data ss:Type="String">{XML_UNITPROPERTIES_STRATEGIC@FOUND_COLONY@SHARED_DESCRIPTION}</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="s62"/><Cell ss:StyleID="s62"/><Cell ss:StyleID="s62"><Data ss:Type="String">50 reputation with the refered race;</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="s62"/></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell ss:StyleID="s62"><Data ss:Type="String">OPERATION_IN_PROGRESS</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="s62"><Data ss:Type="String">NAME</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Operation In Progress</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="s62"><Data ss:Type="String">Operacja w toku</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="s62"/><Cell ss:StyleID="s62"/><Cell ss:StyleID="s62"/><Cell ss:StyleID="s62"/></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell ss:StyleID="s62"><Data ss:Type="String">OPERATION_IN_PROGRESS</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="s62"><Data ss:Type="String">DESCRIPTION</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">This unit is carrying out an operaton, and cannot be moved in the world map.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="s62"><Data ss:Type="String">Ta jednostka wykonuje operację i nie można jej przemieszczać na mapie świata.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="s62"/><Cell ss:StyleID="s62"/><Cell ss:StyleID="s62"/><Cell ss:StyleID="s62"/></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell ss:StyleID="s62"><Data ss:Type="String">FOUND_COLONY_OPERATION</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="s62"><Data ss:Type="String">IN_PROGRESS</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">A colony is being founded here. It will be completed in [INT_duration].</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="s62"><Data ss:Type="String">Tutaj powstaje nowa kolonia. Prace zakończą się za [INT_duration].</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="s62"/><Cell ss:StyleID="s62"/><Cell ss:StyleID="s62"/><Cell ss:StyleID="s62"/></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell ss:StyleID="s62"><Data ss:Type="String"/></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="s62"><Data ss:Type="String"/></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String"/></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="s62"/><Cell ss:StyleID="s62"/><Cell ss:StyleID="s62"/><Cell ss:StyleID="s62"><Data ss:Type="String">In the text below, text refers to a person that can either be male or female. If relevant for translation, please use the ‘localized string’ column for the male text and the ‘alternative localized string’ column for the female text. You and Your might be examples of this.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="s62"/></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell ss:StyleID="s62"><Data ss:Type="String"/></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="s62"><Data ss:Type="String"/></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String"/></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="s62"/><Cell ss:StyleID="s62"/><Cell ss:StyleID="s62"/><Cell ss:StyleID="s62"><Data ss:Type="String">In the text below, any inserted strings - anything of the form {text} - is replaced by an integer value for the thing described in the brackets. If the {text} is not followed by a unit - e.g. shields, hitpoints - the icon for the unit is inserted together with the integer. The same holds for symbols - e.g. '+', '%' - which are occasionally inserted together with the integer.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="s62"/></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell ss:StyleID="s62"><Data ss:Type="String"/></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="s62"><Data ss:Type="String"/></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String"/></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="s62"/><Cell ss:StyleID="s62"/><Cell ss:StyleID="s62"/><Cell ss:StyleID="s62"><Data ss:Type="String">For references to game terminology and in-world references, please check the glossary delivered as part of the documentation.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="s62"/></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell ss:StyleID="s62"><Data ss:Type="String">FOUND_COLONY</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="s62"><Data ss:Type="String">SHARED_DESCRIPTION</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Founds a new colony where your people can live and work.[br/][br/][bulletlist][bullet][warningred]Requires a Colonizer unit[/warningred][/bullet][bullet][abilitygreen]Produce new units and structures[/abilitygreen][/bullet][bullet][abilitygreen]Collect income from the sector[/abilitygreen][/bullet][bullet][abilitygreen]Can annex and collect income from adjacent sectors[/abilitygreen][/bullet][bullet][abilitygreen]Increases your relation with the colony's race[/abilitygreen][/bullet][/bulletlist]</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="s62"><Data ss:Type="String">Zakłada nową kolonię, w której mogą żyć i pracować twoi ludzie.[br/][br/][bulletlist][bullet][warningred]Wymaga jednostki kolonizatora.[/warningred][/bullet][bullet][abilitygreen]Wytwarza nowe jednostki i konstrukcje.[/abilitygreen][/bullet][bullet][abilitygreen]Wytwarza dochód z sektora.[/abilitygreen][/bullet][bullet][abilitygreen]Może przyłączać sąsiednie sektory i zbierać z nich dochody.[/abilitygreen][/bullet][bullet][abilitygreen]Poprawia twoje stosunki z cywilizacją, którą reprezentuje kolonia.[/abilitygreen][/bullet][/bulletlist]</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="s62"/><Cell ss:StyleID="s62"/><Cell ss:StyleID="s62"/><Cell ss:StyleID="s62"/></Row></Table><WorksheetOptions xmlns="urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:excel"><Unsynced/><Selected/><Panes><Pane><Number>3</Number><ActiveRow>23</ActiveRow><ActiveCol>8</ActiveCol></Pane></Panes><ProtectObjects>False</ProtectObjects><ProtectScenarios>False</ProtectScenarios></WorksheetOptions></Worksheet></Workbook>